Imperative: Explicitly describe the actions/Describe HOW the actions should be done/
eg: Painting a house
- Open the can of Painting
- Dip the brush in it 
- Move brush in stroking fashion on the wall
- Telling painter EXACTLY what to do

Declarative: 
eg: Painting a house
- 'Will you please paint the exterior of the house this color?'
- Painter would know what to do without EXACT step by step.  They know how to do the job